quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"The praise/gratitude (is) to God who descended on His worshipper/slave The Book , and He did not make/create for it crookedness/indirectness"
  18,2,"A straight/valuable (Book) to warn/give notice (of) a severe power/might from at Him, and (it) announces good news (to) the believers those who make/do the correct/righteous deeds , that (E) for them (is a) good/beautiful reward"
  18,3,(They) are remaining/residing in it forever/eternally (E)
  18,4,"And He/it warns/gives notice (to) those who said: \"God took/received a child (a son)"
  18,5,"Nothing from knowledge (is) to them with it (they have no knowledge of it) and nor to their fathers, a word/speech/sermon became big (that) emerges from their mouths, that they say except lies/denials/falsifications (about God)"
  18,6,"So maybe/perhaps you (are) exhausting/destroying yourself from anger sorrowfully/angrily on their tracks , if they do not believe with this the information/speech"
  18,7,"We have made/put what (is) on the earth/Planet Earth (as) decoration/beauty for it, to test them which of them (is) better (in) a deed"
  18,8,And We are making/putting (E) what (is) on it destroyed/infertile dust
  18,9,"Or (have) you thought/supposed that (E) the cave`s and The Book`s/inscription`s owners/company , were (in) astonishment/amazement from Our verses/signs/evidences? (Did you think that the cave`s and The Book`s people were strange or amazing)"
  18,10,"When the youths/servants took shelter/refuge to (in) the cave , so they said: \"Our Lord give/bring us from at You mercy and prepare/make possible for us from our matter/affair (a) correct/right guidance"
  18,11,So We stamped/resided/palpitated (refer to in dictionary) on their ears in the cave numerous years
  18,12,Then We sent/resurrected/revived them to know which (of) the two groups/parties (is) more counting/controlling to what time they remained/waited